     2 				;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
     3 				; Memory Map
     4 				;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
     5 				; VBXE RAM Usage ($80 banks, 4kB each)
     6 				; MEMAC_A is set to $2000, with a 4kB window, CPU only
     7
     8 				; VRAM is wasting a tremendous amount of space in order for faster & simpler code
     9 				; Currently, with 256 pixel wide screen:
    10 				;	$00400        = XDL
    11 				;	$00500        = BCBs
    12 				;	$20000        = Screen 1
    13 				;	$40000        = Screen 2
    14 				;	$60000-$72BFF = Colour Map Data
    15
